      "content": "idk i dont think i'm dehydrated... i've been drinking water all day. it just felt so sudden and weirdly intense. do u think it could just be stress or something? i have a huge exam tomorrow so im pretty wired. i really dont want to go to the er if i can help it, it's so expensive and i just need to study.",
